Title: Missing useful macros in reporting
Component: reporting
State: open
Date: 2016-02-26 16:10:46
Targetversion: 1.2.8
Class: nastiness

In a report with single context (e.g. host) there should be a list of
macros available. At least $HOSTNAME$. Otherwise it is impossible to
put the name of the host int the title of the report.
